text: Stefan Thanei (born 3 September 1981) is an Italian freestyle skier. He competed in the 2013, 2015 and 2017 FIS Freestyle World Ski Championships, and in the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:Italian male alpine skiers Category:Italian male freestyle skiers Category:Olympic freestyle skiers of Italy Category:Freestyle skiers at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:People from Schlanders
